  Locus:
    Page: 169
    Verse: 19
Tags:
  - Forgiveness
---
The unforgiving mind sees itself as innocent and others as guilty. It
thrives on conflict and on being right, and it sees inner peace as its enemy.
It perceives everything as separate.
